These are Puzzles for 7x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-2-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, hot-chocolate, milk, sprite
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, september, june, august
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: poppy, aconite, marigold, orchid
There are 4 different favourite colors: white, apricot, aquamarine, grey
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, goldfish, hedgehog, lizard
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, baseball, lacrosse, sailing
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, bus, jet-ski, snowmobile
 1. the person who's birthday is in april is between the person drinking fanta and the owner of the chinchilla##2
 2. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far left##1
 3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person who likes white##1
 4. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
 5. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
 7. the person who likes apricot is between the person driving the bus and the owner of the lizard##2
 8. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in august is the person who likes white##1
10. the person who's sport is baseball is the person who's birthday is in september##1
11. the person who's sport is sailing is the person who growsmarigold##1
12. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
13. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
14. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
15. the person who likes aquamarine is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Beverage      | milk        | sprite     | hot-chocolate | fanta      |
| Birthday          | june | september    | april      | august  |
| Flower         | aconite  | orchid    | poppy       | marigold     |
| Color   | aquamarine        | grey       | apricot          | white |
| Pet           | hedgehog    | chinchilla | goldfish      | lizard     |
| Sport         | badminton   | baseball   | lacrosse      | sailing    |
| Transport     | bike        | bus        | snowmobile    | jet-ski    |

