.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-2-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta, iced-tea, mirinda
4 different games are played: canasta, snooker, go, backgammon
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, camping, rock-climbing, singing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, mystery, scientific, sports
4 different pets are kept: cat, fish, horse, lizard
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, brazilian, indonesian, mexican
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, tiparillo, baccarat, siglo
 1. the person drinking mirinda is the owner of the lizard##1
 2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
 3. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
 4. the indonesian is the owner of the fish##1
 5. the person watching mystery movies is the person playing backgammon##1
 6. the colombian is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1
 7. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
 8. the person playing snooker is the tiparillo-smoker##1
 9. the bolivar-smoker is the person who's hobby is singing##1
10. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
11. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
12. the person playing canasta is between the baccarat-smoker and the person playing go##2
13. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
14. the brazilian is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
15. the siglo-smoker is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3       |       4       |
| Beverage      | mirinda | coffee     | fanta        | iced-tea      |
| Game          | snooker  | go   | canasta    | backgammon        |
| Hobby         | camping | singing    | baking       | rock-climbing |
| Movie-Genre   | sports  | scientific | epic         | mystery       |
| Pet           | lizard  | cat        | fish         | horse         |
| Nationality         | brazilian | mexican   | indonesian | colombian      |
| Cigar     | tiparillo    | bolivar   | siglo        | baccarat        |

